```mermaid
flowchart LR
  main([rpc_remote_client/main.cpp<br/>main()]) --> ws[WebRTCSocket]
  ws --> initSig[WebRTCSocket::_init_signaling()]
  ws --> pcMgr[WebRTCSocket maintains clients:<br/>Map&lt;clientId, ClientPeerConnection&gt;]
  ws -->|create/retain stream| stream[Stream(Video: RemoteProcessStreamSource,<br/>Audio: SilenceOpusSource)]

  stream --> videoSrc[RemoteProcessStreamSource]
  stream --> audioSrc[SilenceOpusSource]

  videoSrc --> producer[producer_loop() produces next media sample]
  producer --> grab[ProcessUiCapture::grab_process_ui_rgb]
  grab --> capSrc[ICaptureSource]
  capSrc -.-> gdiBack[GdiProcessUiCaptureBackend]
  capSrc -.-> dxgiBack[DxgiProcessUiCaptureBackend]

  producer --> sanitize[FrameSanitizer::sanitize_frame()]
  producer --> pacing[FramePacingPolicy::update_and_get_fps()]
  producer --> encode[VideoEncodePipeline::encode_frame()]
  encode --> layout[EncoderLayoutPolicy]
  producer --> outState[SampleOutputState<br/>current_sample + timestamps]

  stream -->|on_sample callback| sender[WebRTCSocket::on_sample]
  sender --> tracks[ClientPeerConnection Track(s)<br/>track->sendFrame(RTP)]

  ws --> inputs[InputController<br/>simulate mouse/keyboard]
  ws --> fileXfer[FileTransferService<br/>file chunk transfer]

  ws --> controlChan[DataChannel(JSON)<br/>frameMark / captureHealth / input / file transfer]
  sender --> rtc[(WebRTC: PeerConnection / Track / DataChannel)]
  pcMgr --> pc[ClientPeerConnection<br/>dispatches DataChannel messages]
  pc -->|input control| inputs
  pc -->|media send| tracks
```

